Package: HTRX
Type: Package
Title: Haplotype Trend Regression with eXtra Flexibility (HTRX)
Version: 1.2.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yaoling", "Yang", email = "yaoling.yang@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
